toi rat buon khi mua dien thoai nay.moi mua chua duoc 1 thang thi nut cam ung tro ve k dc.pin thi bi phu.dua di bao hanh thi bac buoc fai thay luon mang hinh cam ung.gia 1.4tr.con k thay thi tra ve.tui co yeu cau bao hanh cuc pin.thi van tu choi.fai thay mang hinh moi dc bao hanh cuc pin.mn xem thu co chap nhan dc k.tui danh fai nhan lai dien thoai.ve bo luon.hu pin sao sai.con cam ung thi liet phien tro ve toi van sai dc.nhu hu pin thi toi bo tay. 